Business Rules:
BR1: A tour package must include at least one destination (e.g., a city or attraction).
BR2: A tour package can only be deleted by admin users.
BR3: Each tour package must have all required details, such as a name, description, price, cities, countries, etc.

System Requirements:
SYSREQ1: Create a relational table to link tour packages with destinations, ensuring at least one destination exists for each package.
SYSREQ2: Implement a service-layer method to restrict tour package deletion to admin users only.
SYSREQ3: Add validation checks in the service layer to ensure all required details are provided when creating or updating tour packages.
